Dear Community Partner,

On behalf of Councilwoman Angela Reeves and the District 2 office, thank you for the work
GearUp Detroit continues to do with young people in the neighbourhood. This is a routine
quarterly update to our community partners.

WHAT IS COMING UP
- The District 2 Youth Opportunity Fair returns to the recreation center in November.
  Partner tables are free. Let our office know if GearUp would like a spot.
- The city youth-programming survey is open through the end of the month. Participation is
  optional and helps shape next year's grant priorities.
- Our office continues to share partner events on the community calendar. Send us your
  flyers and we will help spread the word.

No response is required to this note. If GearUp would like a table at the fair, just reply
at your convenience and we will hold one.

With appreciation,
Office of Councilwoman Angela Reeves
Detroit City Council, District 2
